"title": "8296: love, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8296",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture offers an understanding of the source, character and value of love, based on the nature and actions of God.</p>\n<h2>God is the source of love</h2>\n<h3>His very character is love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7-1John4:8\">1JN 4:7–4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:12\">1TH 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:7\">2TI 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:16\">1JN 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:19\">1JN 4:19</a></p>\n<h3>The love of God is revealed in the cross of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:10\">1JN 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:2\">EPH 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a></p>\n<h3>Love is part of the Holy Spirit's fruit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30\">ROM 15:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:8\">COL 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>The loving-kindness of God referred to in the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:13\">EXO 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6\">EXO 34:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:42\">2CH 6:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:4\">PSA 6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:10\">PSA 32:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1\">PSA 51:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:43\">PSA 107:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7\">ISA 63:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22\">LAM 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:19\">HOS 2:19</a></p>\n<h2>The love of God in the NT</h2>\n<h3>To describe God's love for humanity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:42\">JHN 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:39\">ROM 8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4\">EPH 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>To describe love for God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:15\">JHN 21:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:3\">1TH 1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:8\">1PE 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:3\">1JN 5:3</a></p>\n<h3>To describe brotherly love</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:35\">JHN 13:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:8\">ROM 13:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:24\">1CO 16:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:8\">2CO 8:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:13\">GAL 5:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:2\">EPH 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9\">PHP 1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:5\">PHM 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>To describe love expressed by eating together</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:13\">2PE 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12\">JUD 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>To describe love in a negative sense</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:43\">LUK 11:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19\">JHN 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:43\">JHN 12:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:10\">2TI 4:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:15\">2PE 2:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15\">1JN 2:15</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:4-1Cor13:8\">1CO 13:4–13:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9\">ROM 12:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:5\">1TI 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22\">1PE 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:18\">1JN 4:18</a></p>\n<h2>Love is shown by deeds</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:17-1John3:18\">1JN 3:17–3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:15\">ROM 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9\">1JN 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:2-1John5:3\">1JN 5:2–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:6\">2JN 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:5-3John1:6\">3JN 1:5–1:6</a></p>\n<h2>The pre-eminence of love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:13\">1CO 13:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37-Matt22:39\">MAT 22:37–22:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:29-Mark12:31\">MRK 12:29–12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:9-Rom13:10\">ROM 13:9–13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:31-1Cor13:3\">1CO 12:31–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:6\">GAL 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:17-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:17–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:14\">COL 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:7\">2PE 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:10\">1JN 2:10</a></p>",
